{"commands": [{"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "\n%md-sandbox\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 0; padding-top: 9px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://databricks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/db-academy-rgb-1200px.png\" alt=\"Databricks Learning\" style=\"width: 1200px\">\n</div>", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "ddde3717-fb70-498e-9cfe-42d65685eaea", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "df967588-6045-4dc2-bd6d-d45282d7120b", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 1, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n<img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/Apache-Spark-Logo_TM_200px.png\" style=\"float: left: margin: 20px\"/>\n\nRead the Stock Orders bronze Delta table. Deduplicate and write the resulting DataFrame to the silver Delta table after executing a few datetime transformations.\n\n# Bronze To Silver - Stock Transactions\n\n## In this exercise you will:\n* Learn how to deduplicate your data using performant Spark API\n* Practice windowing and specifying windows\n* Practice using ranking over windows for deduplication \n* Practice handling and transforming datetime fields with built-in functions like `year`, `month` and others\n\n## Prerequisites\n* Web browser: **Chrome**\n* A cluster configured with **8 cores** and **DBR 7.0**", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "35478f7c-5678-4a9e-9301-9588c79e10e0", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "21cd6e24-13bb-4b45-9252-adb1502ded32", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 2, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Classroom-Setup<br>\n\nFor each lesson to execute correctly, please make sure to run the **`Classroom-Setup`** cell at the start of each lesson (see the next cell) and the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell at the end of each lesson.", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "eccb1932-41ef-49b1-80ad-6b0aa6a8b371", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "8dcffd78-ae0e-4e23-9b7f-46ed6bf5b32c", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 3, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%run ./Includes/PCF-11S-ClassroomSetup", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "308c1340-ca10-4508-b010-fe9f7f7af96e", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "0618ad38-be54-46d5-bd27-25b30786830a", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 4, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Steps to complete<br>\nImplement the **`challenge()`** function to achieve the following:\n\n- Read the Stock Orders table from **`bronzeStockOrdersPath`** into a DataFrame.\n- Drop duplicates: some stock orders (**`transaction_id`**) have been duplicated - for each **`transaction_id`**, keep the oldest one by using **`ordertime`** (hint: use window and rank functions). Assign the result to a new variable name and do the transformations described below.\n- Currently **`ordertime`** is in unixtime format. Create a new column named **`order_timestamp`** from the **`ordertime`** column by converting it to timestamp.\n- There are useful built-in functions in Spark. Here we can use some of them:\n- Create a new column named **`year`** from the **`order_timestamp`** column, which shows the year.\n- Create a new column named **`month`** from the **`order_timestamp`** column, which shows the month.\n- Create a new column named **`day`** from the **`order_timestamp`** column, which shows the day.\n- Create a new column named **`dow`** from the **`order_timestamp`** column, which shows the day of the week.\n- Write the resulting DataFrame to **`targetDirectory`** as a Delta table using the overwrite mode.\n\n**`bronzeStockOrdersPath`** and **`targetDirectory`** have already been defined in your environment.\n\nThe resulting DataFrame schema should look like this:\n\n|name|type|\n|---|---|\n|clicked_items|ArrayType(ArrayType(StringType,true),true)|\n|investor|LongType|\n|ordertime|LongType|\n|price|DoubleType|\n|ticker|StringType|\n|transaction_id|LongType|\n|type|StringType|\n|volume|LongType|\n|order_timestamp|TimestampType|\n|year|IntegerType|\n|month|IntegerType|\n|day|IntegerType|\n|dow|IntegerType|", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "3369dbe9-3920-4ecf-9e8e-27cee4cd30a5", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "ff95f5ad-9e9f-4465-9ff6-4f8f0f3c7bab", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 5, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// TODO\n\ndef challenge(spark:org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession, bronzeStockOrdersPath:String, targetDirectory:String ) : DataFrame = {\n\n  // `transaction_id` column in `stockOrders` has duplicates - keep the oldest one by `ordertime` (hint: windowing), assign it to a new variable name.\n  \n  // Create a new column named `order_timestamp` from the `ordertime` column by converting it to timestamp.\n  // Extract the year from `order_timestamp` into the `year` column.\n  // Extract the month from `order_timestamp` into the `month` column.\n  // Extract the day of month from `order_timestamp` into the `day` column.\n  // Extract the day of week from `order_timestamp` into the `dow` column.\n  \n  // Write the resulting DataFrame to `targetDirectory` as a Delta table using the overwrite mode and overwrite schema option.\n  \n  // Return the resulting DataFrame:\n\n  return FILL_IN.DATAFRAME\n}\n\nval finalDF = challenge(spark, bronzeStockOrdersPath, targetDirectory)\ndisplay(finalDF)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "2632f6aa-01ae-4cb3-abfc-f1ede96fbf78", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "4273be54-533c-4df0-a8b2-4d6f5c071044", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 6, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n<h2><img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png